,(15,'招聘信息','婚艺网','招聘','1430035431','0','','','','<p>招聘<br/></p>','0','招聘','','0'),(16,'6款经典婚纱','婚艺网','婚纱','1432550166','1','data/upload/7b5dcecb6060f5a9e508b4051d2ee899.jpg','1','1','<p><br/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 婚纱是一段记忆，也是每个女孩子的梦。童话中的公主就是穿着美丽的蓬蓬裙，永远都是最美丽的一面。每个女孩子都有一个梦想，梦想自己永远都是世界的焦点，有一个永远爱护自己的男人。拥有一件漂亮的婚纱对我来说有着非凡的意义！虽说一辈子只能穿一次，但就算是躺在衣柜里，我时不时想起来看看它，摸摸它，也能回想起当时的感动。在国外，有的人甚至会把婚纱礼服留给自己的女儿当传家宝，也真的有新娘是穿自己妈妈的婚纱结婚，当然婚纱是修改过的，加加减减，复古和创新集聚一身。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<strong style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(112,48,160); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">关于婚纱的款式有很多，小编结合国外国内婚纱市场，整理了以下6款经典婚纱供新娘选择。</span></strong></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">A-line (A字型剪裁)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100448138747.jpg\" alt=\"2_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100448138747.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　这是大多准新娘都会选择的款式，优雅大方。对自己身材比较没自信或是担心大腿比较粗壮的姑娘们可以考虑A字型剪裁，因为它可以完美的遮掩掉你下半身的缺陷。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">ball gown (公主式散裙)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100458120252.jpg\" alt=\"3_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100458120252.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">很多甜美小巧的新娘都喜欢这种款式的婚纱，很适合花园婚礼或是非常梦幻的婚礼。我的好朋友就是把这种公主式的散裙改短变成像是短款的礼服，前短后长，露出美腿，反响超赞。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">cap sleeves (灯笼袖)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100463694963.jpg\" alt=\"4_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100463694963.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">灯笼袖是我认为最有气质的一款婚纱，很适合长相有些古典气质的新娘，也非常适合外国人。很多块头比较大的明星在结婚的时候也都选择了灯笼袖的婚纱，因为可以修饰A字膊，也可以让上半身看起来纤细些。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">Sweetheart cut (新型领口)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100467560661.jpg\" alt=\"5_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100467560661.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">心型领口很适合脖子比较短一些的新娘，它可以让颈部的线条更妹更修长。另外，它胸口的设计可以突出胸部的线条，是一款很性感的婚纱。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">Mermaid(美人鱼)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100490111262.jpg\" alt=\"6_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100490111262.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　<br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">这款婚纱就是我们俗称的鱼尾款，也是我梦想中的婚纱。鱼尾的线条非常迷人，可以完美展现女人的曲线。但是它的缺点就是上身完全都是包身的设计，所以如果腰部线条不够完美穿出来就会显得臃肿。</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　<span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">Chapel(拖尾款式)</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432100481268561.jpg\" alt=\"7_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150520/1432100481268561.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">大部分的婚纱都可以做拖尾款，有拖尾的婚纱看起来非常高贵。</span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"/></p><p><br/></p>','1','婚纱是一段记忆，也是每个女孩子的梦。童话中的公主就是穿着美丽的蓬蓬裙，永远都是最美丽的一面。每个女孩子都有一个梦想，梦想自己永远都是世界的焦点，有一个永远爱护自己的男人。拥有一件漂亮的婚纱对我来说有着非凡的意义！虽说一辈子只能穿一次，但就算是躺在衣柜里，我时不时想起来看看它，摸摸它，也能回想起当时的感动。在国外，有的人甚至会把婚纱礼服留给自己的女儿当传家宝，也真的有新娘是穿自己妈妈的婚纱结婚，当然婚纱是修改过的，加加减减，复古和创新集聚一身。','data/images/7b5dcecb6060f5a9e508b4051d2ee899_thumb.jpg','0'),(17,'12条必看的婚纱购买大全','婚艺网','婚纱','1432102150','1','data/upload/226425d251c15d7a7935c1d9d2229723.jpg','1','1','<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px 20px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><a style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: none; COLOR: rgb(0,153,204)\" href=\"http://www.wmpic.me/52301/555af8e3d8a4d_57\"></a></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px 20px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><a style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: none; COLOR: rgb(0,153,204)\" href=\"http://www.wmpic.me/52301/555af8f94238e_38\"></a></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">1、计算成本</strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">当你在计算你的婚纱预算时，别忘了加上头纱、头花鞋、内衣和婚礼首饰等等这些小东西的费用。如果你购买的不是量身定制的婚纱，别忘了把修改婚纱这部分费用预留出来。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">2、考虑场地</strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">场地跟婚纱的搭配很重要，如果你在酒店举办婚礼，就选择隆重闪亮的婚纱；如果你选择户外婚礼，那就选择简单轻盈的婚纱款式；有一些教堂认为露肩是不礼貌的行为，所以在买婚纱之前，考虑下婚礼场地跟婚纱的搭配吧。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">3、选择工作日去买婚纱</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最好能选择一个工作日去买婚纱，相比人多拥挤的周六而言，你会获得销售人员很多的关注和时间。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">4、如何节省费用</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 避免挑选太过华丽的款式，比方那些缀满珠饰和很多花边点缀的。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">通常试穿或者橱窗陈列样衣有可能可以特价。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"></strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">5、别限制款式选择</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;先不要着急排除那些你乍一看就觉得不合适的款，就算你很清楚什么是最适合你的款，也不要让思维定势太限制你的选择。不如多试试，各种款式和颜色，然后再根据哪种颜色和款式你串起来最漂亮来决定。所以当服务小姐给你推荐那些“你一定要试试”的款式，务必从善如流地去试穿，就算你不喜欢它挂在衣架上的样子。请相信，这些服务人员看过很多新娘试婚纱，她们的经验对你来说，很有帮助。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"></strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">6、别着急买第一件婚纱</strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">你不是第一次约会就会订婚，对吧？同样的道理，不要买你试穿的第一款婚纱。所以在买之前，一定给自己多点时间再多点考虑再多点选择，多逛逛，一个一个店地仔细逛逛。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">7、即使选定了，也过一夜再说</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp; 就算你已经挑中了满意的婚纱，也要再花些时间考虑清楚，是不是真的就是你最想要的。特别是定制婚纱，大部分婚纱店的购买守则里都加上“不能退货”的条款，就算你能拿回来些钱，也最多最多不会超过50%。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"></strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">8、相信你的直觉</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果你需要反复确认那款婚纱你穿起来是不是漂亮，那这件往往就不会是你的那件。穿起来是不是你想象当中自己当新娘的样子？你能不能看到自己穿着这款婚纱走在红毯上的情景？如果答案不是肯定的，赶紧脱掉继续挑吧。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">9、量好尺寸</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp; 当你准备好去定制婚纱时，婚纱店会帮你量精确的尺寸：胸围、腰围和臀围。每个制造商都有自己的尺码尺寸表，他们会根据各自的标准来定义你的尺寸。一个有经验的婚纱店会知道每一件婚纱都渴望被人穿得合身漂亮。<br/>爱结提示：务必也请他们教你看看他们的尺码表，以便更清楚知道自己的尺寸。确认你真的预订的是最合适的尺寸，即使偏大也不能偏小。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"></strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">10、保持身材</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp; 你肯定也知道，每件婚纱都会要根据你的身型修改到最合身最服帖。所以当你的婚纱修改好了以后，务必确保你的身材每个部位都一直保持原样。<br/><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\">婚艺365提示：对于改婚纱而言，腰围和长度是比较容易的；而相对来说，袖子的改动，束身上衣的改动，花边或珠饰的增加等，都是比较复杂的改动了。</span></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"></strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">11、内衣选择</strong><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 婚纱设计师建议大家穿跟肤色最接近的内衣。这样能最大限度让它隐身，也比较不会有透过婚纱看见内衣的尴尬。</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">12、充足时间</strong></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">你大概会有两三款礼服的配置，所以当你购买婚纱之前应该先和店家确认好时间表；也许你还需要更多，所以一定要留出来充足的时间备用。<br/><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\">婚艺提示：鉴于修改婚纱很经常是额外需要的步骤，所以你在买的时候还需要问一下修改可能需要的时间。如果该店不提供修改服务，问问售货人员他们是否有经常合作或者推荐的可信赖的裁缝。</span></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(43,43,43); TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 14px/23px 宋体, serif; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 2em; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></p><p style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COL