AP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">有一个好的化妆师会为你增色不少</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">，不仅在妆容上能让你达到最美的姿态，在服饰和发型的设计上也会为之增色不少。都说女孩当新娘子是最美的时候，所以这一点很重要，化妆师画成凤姐，估计请再好的摄影师、摄像师也拍不出范冰冰。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">化妆地点也很重要，尽量在光线较好的地方</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">，这样化妆师和摄影、摄像都会达到最好的效果。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432032974491853.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150519/1432032974491853.jpg\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">2. 婚礼的舞台和灯光</strong></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">婚礼的舞台豪华或者简单都不是最重要的问题，如果舞台很大很奢华，要想为之呈现当时的现场，就要相应配好灯光，因为</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">只有灯光到位，才能看出舞台的效果</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">，如果是个布置并不复杂的舞台，只要灯光运用的得当，也会得到非常好的现场效果哦。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">新人有时拿到照片会发现总有人脸黑一块亮一块，这就是灯光不到位，导致光分布的不均匀。还有人发现脸的颜色不是红色，就是紫色，这也是因为脸上打了有颜色的灯，这个灯导致皮肤的颜色不正常，所以建议新人</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">尽量不要运用有颜色的追光</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">，这样摄影师和摄像师后期都没法补救，除非黑白片。当然如果是室外办的婚礼就不存在这个问题啦，这个就要看个人喜好。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432033326173073.jpg\" alt=\"635675522330411250_副本.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150519/1432033326173073.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">3. 摄影和摄像</span></strong></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">婚礼摄影很多新人可能都觉得就是拍照片的，对，摄影师就是拍照片的，但婚礼当天的所有人的情绪，状态，心情都是可以从照片中去感受的，一个好的摄影师是可以用照片来讲述故事的，可以让你十年后看到照片依旧能感受到婚礼当天的感动，每一个你看不到的细节可能摄影师已经帮你记录在相机内了，所以纪实是婚礼最重要的，那天你可以</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">放肆的笑，任意的哭，最好可以当摄影师不存在</span><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">，尽情的去享受婚礼当天的所有，剩下的交给你信任的摄影师。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">摄像是动态的，当天所有的影像都被记录在内，好的摄像师会把婚礼拍成一个电影，而主角和故事是只属于你们的。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><img title=\"1432033439124766.jpg\" alt=\"20130327114219539.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/20150519/1432033439124766.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">婚礼是一辈子的事儿，所以为自己不留遗憾，认真准备一场值得回味的婚礼吧。</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; CLEAR: both; MARGIN: 0px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"/></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p>','1,7,8,9','一场完美婚礼由众多因素决定，但在这，要帮大家做到能做到的最好的。','data/images/c8414d2705988449cbd8491c5924b0dc_thumb.jpg','0'),(23,'10个婚礼筹备雷区，新人小心绕行！','婚艺网','筹备，婚礼，新人','1432030370','1','data/upload/41a2f4aaaec1bf50a23f81897916c1f2.jpg','1','1','<br/><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">为了让自己的婚礼添色加彩，很多新人会动用各种方式苦苦找寻适合自己婚礼的英文歌曲。<strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">大家不用苦恼啦，小编为你准备了私藏已久的35首感人婚礼英文歌曲，现在需要做的就是跟我一起来感受歌曲的浪漫吧。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\"><br/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">1. The rose</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">爱尔兰男团西城男孩的嗓音柔和温婉，最适合在婚礼上做背景音乐，一首传唱多年的经典老歌，那句“I say love, It is a flower, and you it&#39;s only seed。”“我说，爱是一朵花，而你是唯一的种子。”不知拨动了多少人的心弦。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">2. Could this be love</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">这是一首很适合翩翩起舞的歌曲，虽然是首老歌，也没有新的翻唱版本，但这种复古的感觉不是更能给婚礼带来一丝永恒的感觉吗？Jennifer Lopes在伴奏部分诺诺自语“El Amor No Hace Promesas”“爱，无需诺言”，更添加了一份浪漫。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">3. Endless love</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">哪有什么比凝视爱人双眼说上一句“You will always be my endless love。”更催泪的呢。不要怪小编不潮，老是找老歌给大家听，这首可是难得一见的煽情催泪弹。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">4. Way back into love</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">电影《K歌情人》的插曲，这不像前面哭哭滴滴的苦情歌，是一首活泼可爱的小情歌，男女对唱，诉说着找到了对方为自己的生活带来了不一样的色彩。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">5. Nothing</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">’s gonna change my love for you</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">你可能要说这首有那么多版本要用哪首呢？小编攥起拳头力顶Khalil Fong，这首翻唱与原曲的编曲有很大区别，颇有圆舞曲的风范，小号和风琴融合为一，饱满而浪漫。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">6. Can</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">’t take my eyes off you</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">一首充满蛊惑的歌，有好些电影桥段用来做背景音乐，表现受尽婚姻折磨的男主人公遇见小情人的场景。没错这首就是这般张扬地表达了君子见到窈窕淑女时的原始冲动。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">7. Angels</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">坏小子Robbie Williams能被什么样的天使救赎呢？竟然能让他说出对她的爱是“I’m loving angels instead。”“我爱着的是天使。”你的那个姑娘是不是也是这样一位塑造了你的天使呢？</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">8. Halo</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">这首不荐对不起自己，对不起大家。Beyonce和Jay Z是圈里有名的模范夫妻，这首歌更是两人爱情的见证。看到爱人的头顶被光环笼罩着，他闪闪发光牵着你走过黑暗。Beyonce毫不吝啬自己的好唱功，声情并茂，令人动容。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">9. When a man loves a woman</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">只要第一句“When a man loves a woman”想起，我保准你也会说似曾相识。Michael Bolton沧桑的嗓音好像月老看着情人牵手，感慨万千，千言万语化成了这首歌曲。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">10. This love</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">这首集万千宠爱于一身的歌，很有点在ball上的感觉，大家都能即刻起身扭动起来。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">11. And i love you so</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">小编最最爱的被N多人翻唱过的经典情歌。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">12. I know i loved you</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">深情的歌词搭配上优美的旋律，再加上Darren温柔的歌声，百里挑一的组合。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">13. Wedding march</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">经典的行礼音乐又怎少得了？如果不在教堂行礼的新人，可以选择这首歌，令这场婚宴于庄严又隆重的气氛下开始。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#3E3E3E\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">14. Just the Way You Are</span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">同样由Diana Krall重新以Jazz音乐演奏这首经典名曲，又是另一番味道。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:&