: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一、媒体广告</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　在众多的婚庆公司中进行挑选，参考媒体广告的确是快捷方便的办法。通过广告可以明了婚庆公司的定位和特色，还可以了解一些优惠和促销信息。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　1、了解婚庆公司强项</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　婚庆公司的广告中主打的部分虽然是该公司最擅长的服务项目，但却不一定是新人最想要的，所以看的时候要注意舍取，不要挑花眼。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、看看服务是否有新意</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　婚礼也是种时尚， 新鲜感很重要，试着把几期杂志中同一公司的广告做个纵向比较，看看有没有不断更新的新鲜内容和时髦创意。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">二、亲朋好友推荐</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　婚庆是个很特别的服务行业，往往没有现成的样品供新人选择，所以此时操办过婚事的亲朋好友的意见就显得尤为重要，成功也好， 失败也罢， 他们总能告诉您选择婚庆公司时要注意的要点和诀窍。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　1、参加婚礼时多留心</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　即将结婚的您一定不能放过任何考察婚庆公司的机会，参加朋友婚礼的时候，从会场布置、婚礼节目策划到整个气氛的协调，做个全方位的考察吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　2、适合自己最重要</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　也许你会为朋友的婚礼所感染，因为朋友的衷心推荐而动心，但是记住，适合自己的才是最好的，无论如何一定要自己亲自去和婚庆公司详细沟通之后才能做最后定论。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　三、公司特色</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　新人对婚礼的要求多种多样，有的要省心，有的要个性，而</span><a href=\"http://www.lilywed.cn/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">婚庆公司</a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">也有大有小，有不同的市场定位，所以新人在进行考评的时候就要开始根据“公司特色”进行第一轮选择。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　1、服务和策划最“特色”</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　策划体现个性，服务能让人安心，面对任何婚庆公司这两方面都要先进行考察，新人在最初的咨询阶段就要打听清楚婚庆公司的运作流程、策划过程和服务跟踪机制等。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、细节显特长</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　每个婚庆公司都有些特别擅长的项目，大到会场布置，婚礼摄影摄像，小到喜糖的设计、花的扎制方法，新娘当天的化妆，新人可以根据自己的心头所好进行衡量筛选。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 瀹嬩綋; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　俗话说结婚是人生中最幸福的时刻，所以一定要举行一场浪漫而富有回忆的婚礼，那么打造婚礼的完美也需要新人多动头脑，首先选择婚庆公司的技巧必须要把握，上边也做了介绍，希望准新人在筹备婚礼时可以用的到哦。(转载自百合婚嫁社区）</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','每个婚庆公司都有些特别擅长的项目，大到会场布置，婚礼摄影摄像，小到喜糖的设计、花的扎制方法，新娘当天的化妆，新人可以根据自己的心头所好进行衡量筛选。','data/images/3e08e3437befaecfc721f23af2073cc9_thumb.jpg','0'),(43,'读完这些内容 巧省婚礼费用','婚艺网','婚礼费用','1436233704','1','data/upload/f35957decc1c125695a149559731aaa0.jpg','1','1','<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14px\"><img title=\"201506121434100444468120.jpg\" alt=\"201392620199493.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/201506121434100444468120.jpg\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">婚礼筹备省钱妙招一：自己买婚纱</span></strong></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　　目前，新娘婚礼的三件套</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">——</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">婚纱、晚礼服、旗袍，市场租赁起步价是</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">1200</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">元。如果准新人去批发市场购买婚纱的话，用</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">1000</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">元的价钱就可以买下质量款式都满意的三件套。</span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　<strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">　婚礼筹备省钱妙招二：中午办婚典</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　　由于办婚宴的人多，酒店相对紧张，巧打时间差办婚礼能省下一大笔开支。如果准新人们选择在酒店不太紧张的中午办婚典的话，酒店免收婚庆场地费和婚宴服务费，光这两项就能省下近万元。再加上新人提前一年预订婚宴，价格比现在市场价每桌便宜</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">200</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">元。</span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　<strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">　婚礼筹备省钱妙招三：团购结婚用品</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　　结婚用品种类繁多，单独购买不仅费时费力价格也高。准新人们可以网上加入团购，与其他准备结婚的新人一起组团购买各种婚庆用品。小到请帖、气球，大到婚宴饮料，都能按批发价拿货，让新人省了不少钱。</span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　<strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">　婚礼筹备省钱妙招四：自带婚纱拍婚照</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　　在拍摄婚纱照的时候，自己配备购买的服装，因为不用穿影楼的婚纱，少花了五六百元的租赁费。婚礼过后，再将婚纱折价卖给影楼或婚纱租赁店，又可以得到获得相应的收益。这样下来，一场既时尚又省钱的婚礼就完成了。</span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND: white\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">　　筹备婚礼的省钱方法新人你学会了吗</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">?</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">当然自己也可以</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">DIY</span><span style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14px\">婚礼策划</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14px\">方案，让婚礼真正做到省钱，而且又不失新意，希望上边的四点可以带给新人更多更准确的帮助，使新人拥有一场完美而浪漫的婚礼，轻松享受人生中最甜蜜最幸福的时刻。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"display:none;\" data-background=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8db3e2; BACKGROUND-REPEAT: no-repeat; BACKGROUND-POSITION: center center\"><br/></p>','0','结婚是人生中最幸福的事情，首先筹备婚礼是新人们所重视的，找一家好的婚庆公司为之筹备当然省心，但是想让婚礼筹备更加省钱就需要新人自己动手去准备，下边为新人介绍了婚礼筹备的4个妙招新意省钱法，一起来看看吧，希望带给新人更多的帮助。','data/images/f35957decc1c125695a149559731aaa0_thumb.jpg','0'),(44,'武侠风格婚礼  司仪开场很重要','婚艺网','婚礼创意','1434101231','1','data/upload/8a935ef182550d4aa6477bb7bab918e4.jpg','1','1','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><img src=\"/data/upload/201506121434100931421038.jpg\" title=\"201506121434100931421038.jpg\" alt=\"20140313163316-1940646330.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">因为新郎有着浓浓的武侠情结</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">所以</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">为他量身定做了这场主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">因时间匆忙</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">还有很不完善的地方</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">敬请各位新人及同行提出宝贵意见及批评指导</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　时间</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">:2012</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　婚礼地点</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">:***</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">园</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　策划人主持人</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">:***</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　<strong>　正式文稿</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\">　　<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：小天使温馨提示</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">+</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">男声大气开场</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\">　　<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">先生，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">小姐情定江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">主题婚礼现在开始。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\">　　<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：大气武侠音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　天高云淡江湖情</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">荡气回肠在武林</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">话说射雕大侠郭靖及其夫人黄蓉率丐帮众弟子除奸铲恶</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">声望享誉武林</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">其弟子遍布江南塞北</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">一日</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">皇帝之女</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主出外游玩</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">偶遇一青年侠客</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">二人遂生爱意</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">皇帝为完成公主心愿即命郭靖、黄蓉寻找这位青年侠客。夫妇二人立刻飞鸽传书，把此事告知南北武林盟主</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">并发出英雄帖，召集各大门派。一时间，少林、武当、峨嵋、崆峒、华山、青城、昆仑、恒山等齐聚丐帮，商议寻找青年侠客。但众人只知青年侠客姓</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">名</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，其武功出神入化，为人侠骨柔情、侠肝义胆。郭靖、黄蓉遂做出决定，以华山论剑为由，在华山之颠，由</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主做镇，并暗地通知佛教中人四处打探，以求引出青年侠客</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">一切尽在周密安排</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　时光如梭，话说华山论剑当日，只见华山云集中原及塞北各派武林人士。青年侠客隐身于山林之间，只等郭靖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">\\</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">黄蓉率众武林人士掌声雷动，并大声喊出</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“3.2.1&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">的时候</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">再考虑是否现身与</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主相会</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">各位前辈</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">大侠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">侠女</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">下面</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">就让我们大声的喊出</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">3.2.1,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">看看青年侠客是否会出现于华山之颠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">好吗</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">?</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请你们用掌声来告诉我一下</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">好不好</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">?</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　下面</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">就让我们请出青年侠客</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">***</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">上场</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">3.2.1.(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">3)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　首先</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">大侠向各位武林人士打个招呼</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　有请</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：情醉</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　春沟水动茶花白，夏谷云生荔枝红。青裙玉面如相识，九月茶花满路开。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\">　　<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">大侠还等什么</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">现在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请你去迎接</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">大侠和</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主登上华山之颠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：武侠音乐</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　青年侠客与公主终于来到了华山之颠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中原及塞北武林各大门派掌门人早已在此守候</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">这正是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">:</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　天涯红尘总关情</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">华山之颠正相逢，人声鼎沸旌旗动</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">尽述心中儿女情。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　青年侠客</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">不但武功高强</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">且医术精湛</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">现工作于大庆</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">医院</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在武林中号称</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">&quot;*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">神医</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">&quot;.**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主现工作于大庆市公安局</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">分局</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在武林中人送外号</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">警界侠女</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">&quot;.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">今日二人成婚</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">实乃武林之中天大喜事</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">此刻正是良辰美景</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请新人交换你们的定情信物</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　好的</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">定情信物代表你们对婚姻的尊重和对爱情的承诺</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">那在我们中华文明的艺术宝库里</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">新人在新婚时</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">也要喝上一杯交杯酒</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">交杯酒</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：这是我国婚礼程序中的一个传统仪节，在古代又称为</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">合卺</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">酒</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">合卺也代表结婚的意思。表示新人要永远相爱</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">但是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在请我们今天的新人喝交杯酒之前</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">首先</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请大家欣赏一个表演</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　感谢来自于北京的调酒大师丁磊先生</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">现在摆在新人面前的这两杯交杯酒</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">融合着传统的文化和现代的理念</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">现在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请新人端起</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　携书弹剑走黄沙，瀚海天山处处家。大漠西风飞翠羽，江南八月看桂花。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　此时此刻</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">美酒掺着幸福掌握在你们的手中</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">想想现在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">想想未来</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">想想你们相爱和奋斗的感慨</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请你们喝下此酒</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">以壮英雄美人之色</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　百战江湖一笛横，风雷侠烈死生轻。鸳鸯有耦春蚕若，白马鞍边笑靥生。今日</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">南北武林盟主也亲临现场。下面就让我们请出南北武林盟主，来自于</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">前辈上场为新人代天地证婚</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请新人向南北武林盟主施大礼表示感谢</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　各位大侠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">各位朋友</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">我们常常在问</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">什么是武林</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">什么是江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">?</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">我想</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有人的地方就是武林</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有人的地方就是江湖。但是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在江湖上做一个武林人士首先要有情有义</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">因为</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有情有义是江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　父母恩情，是赋予生命，养育之恩，百善孝为先</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中华民族推崇孝道，江湖亦如此。下面</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">大侠和</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">公主的父母上台</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　首先</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请父亲</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">先生致辞</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">下面</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有请女方亲友团的代表</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">新娘的大哥</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">**</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">先生致辞</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请新人向父母鞠躬表示你们的感恩</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　友谊，在江湖上最看得起的两个字便是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">‘</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">朋友</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">’</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，一句朋友，笑泯恩仇，一句朋友，如同兄弟</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在《天龙八部》里我们看到了乔峰，虚竹，段誉，生死相依，豪气盖天的兄弟之情。从小青梅竹马是朋友，化敌为友，萍水相逢是朋友，路见不平，拔刀相助是朋友，是敌亦是友。一句朋友饱含太多太多，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">‘</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">朋友</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">’</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">两字何值千金，有了朋友就有了生命，有了朋友就有了知己，有了朋友</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">也就有了今天一对新人华山相逢</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">情定江湖。下面请新人向各位江湖上的朋友深深的鞠躬以示谢意</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　刚刚我们说有情有义是江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">那是否还有另外一种江湖呢</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">?</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">我来告诉大家</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">其实</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">爱情也是江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\">　　<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">问世间情为何物，真叫人生死相许</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，爱情就是江湖，爱情就是人生。人如果眼中没有了爱情，就没有江湖。段誉千里追寻王语嫣，乔峰终身不娶为阿朱，李莫愁因爱生恨，令狐冲痛失挚爱，却另拾良缘。多少对英雄美女立下至死不渝的爱情誓言，为了恪守若言，终其一生，爱情的魅力就在于此。在他们眼中一切都是为了爱而存在。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　所以说</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">这就是江湖，不是江湖中的爱情，而是爱情中的江湖，因为</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">爱情就是江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　现在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请新人相对而立</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">从此以后</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">江湖上不论有再多的风雨</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">有再多的风浪</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">你们都在携手一起去闯</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">现在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">请李春雨大侠向后退一步</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">在你和文辉公主以后的生活中</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">如果你们遇到烦恼和争吵</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">就请你能像刚才这样</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">退一步海阔天空</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">&quot;,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">用你的男人的胸怀包容文辉公主的一切</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">同时</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">也请文辉公主能理解你对面这个男人</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">给他空间</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">让他在江湖上自由的驰骋。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　各位来宾，各位朋友，下面我宣布：大侠</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">***</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，公主</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">***</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">正式结为夫妇，爱在</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">系列主题婚礼之</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">情定江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">到此礼成。有请新人手牵手，走下华山之颠，走向武林</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">走向江湖</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">你们幸福的婚姻生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 25px;background-color: white\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">　　新人朋友们为了让自己的婚礼更加完美，婚礼主持词的小小细节也不容错过。（本文转自百合婚礼社区）</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>','0','因为新郎有着浓浓的武侠情结,所以,为他量身定做了这场主题婚礼,因时间匆忙,还有很不完善的地方,敬请各位新人及同行提出宝贵意见及批评指导.','data/images/8a935ef182550d4aa6477bb7bab918e4_thumb.jpg','0'),(45,'婚礼用车的讲究新人知多少','婚艺网','婚礼用车','1434101921','1','data/upload/d14fbfd5a59ed981905cc25389f8b074.jpg','1','1','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体\"><img src=\"/data/upload/201506121434101862511488.jpg\" title=\"201506121434101862511488.jpg\" alt=\"58f783cb39dbb6fdda3499cb0924ab18962b3798.jpg\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体\">一、婚庆用车的选择</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　婚庆用车是现代时尚婚礼的重头戏。一般来说，结婚车人由</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">辆主车组成。接新娘的头车要上档次的好车，一般是加长的凯迪拉克、加长林肯，或者奔驰等。问题是，这些汽车都适合任何一对新人吗</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">?</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">当然不是，从风水看，不同汽车适应不同的人，需要基于五行的考虑。比如，美国车五行属金，德国车五行属火，日本车五行属木，中国车五行属土，部分欧洲车五行属水。因此，在挑选头车时，首先要考虑的是跟新郎、新娘的五行相吻合的国度的车。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　<strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">二、婚庆用车的路线</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　婚礼用车选择线路是有相当风水讲究的。必须避开沿途有医院、寺庙教学、官府机构、高压线、大烟囱以及各类严重的争气之地。一个真实的故事，一位朋友的婚礼用车线路经过某医院，结果，非常不巧的是摄像机将一灵车摄进去了，结果婚后不久新娘就住院了，一直身体不佳。北京也曾有一对新人婚车经过南三环时，遭遇堵车，坐在第二辆车的岳父下车查看情况，却不料被头车突然倒车接到，当场身亡。婚礼变成了葬礼。有心人后来发现事故现场附近是严重的剪刀煞和枪煞。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　<strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">三、婚庆用车的颜色</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　为了和谐起见，如果新郎新娘能在挑选婚庆用车的国别和颜色上五行一致，那自然更好</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">但是往往不一致，比如新郎五行属金、新娘属水，那么，可以照顾新郎五行属金挑选美国车加长的凯迪拉克，而在车的颜色挑选上，照顾新娘的五行属水，挑选黑色的凯迪拉克，这样，两人的五行都能兼顾。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　<strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">四、新人上下婚车的风水</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　从风水来看，头车人员的下车顺序也有讲究。新郎和新娘以一左一右分坐在婚礼头车后排座椅，伴郎一般坐在副驾驶位置，当头车到达婚宴场地时，首先是伴郎下车，从车尾绕至左后门替新郎开门，新郎再从车头绕至右后门替新娘开门，并搀扶新娘下车。这是基于</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">左青龙，右白虎</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">的风水考虑，不能颠倒。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left: 0;line-height:25px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">　　经过上述对于婚庆婚车的小细节了解来看，婚礼的头炮一定要打得响亮哦</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">!（本文转自百合婚礼社区）</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','婚庆用车是现代时尚婚礼的重头戏。一般来说，结婚车人由8辆主车组成。接新娘的头车要上档次的好车，一般是加长的凯迪拉克、加长林肯，或者奔驰等。','data/images/d14fbfd5a59ed981905cc25389f8b074_thumb.jpg','0'),(46,'2015结婚吉